metadata.name: Manipura
metadata.description:
Her life determines whether you can recognize your true desires. She is your status, career, money, and accomplishments. 
She is a powerful, status woman. She knows how to get things done and is good at handling any of her emotions. She's successful, she's rich, and she knows her worth.

What are you without her?

This is the first of 7 works in the Chakras collection. 1/1 NFT.
I can send a physical painting (acrylic on the canvas) if the buyer wishes.

Art size 3015x4500 px
